PRIVACY POLICY FOR PUSH BOX ON APPLE VISION PRO (VISIONOS)

Push Box is a game developed by MESHY for visionOS on Apple Vision Pro. We prioritize your privacy and are committed to complying with all applicable privacy regulations, including the European Union’s General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR). Push Box is designed for an entirely offline, solo experience, and no internet connection is required to play. The game does not collect, process, or transmit any personal information, gameplay data, or statistics.

COMMITMENT TO CONFIDENTIALITY

MESHY is dedicated to safeguarding your privacy while you use Push Box on Apple Vision Pro. Below are the key points of our privacy policy:

Confidential Information
“Confidential Information” refers to any data or information exchanged between MESHY and the user in any form. However, Push Box does not request, collect, or receive any information from players. Consequently, no personal data is gathered by Push Box.

Ownership and Use of Data
All aspects of your experience within Push Box remain entirely private to you. Because the game operates offline, no data is transmitted, sold, or monetized in any form. Additionally, no third-party services or providers receive any information regarding your gameplay.

Duration of the Agreement
This privacy policy takes effect the moment you download and install Push Box. Its terms remain in force for as long as you use the game. Since Push Box does not collect any data, your privacy remains fully protected at all times.

Governing Law and Jurisdiction
This privacy policy is governed by the laws applicable in your country of residence. Any disputes related to this policy will be handled under the relevant legal jurisdictions.

USER RIGHTS & DATA PROTECTION

Because Push Box does not collect, store, or process any personal data, there is no personal information under MESHY’s control. This means:

You have full control over all aspects of your usage data, as none is ever collected or retained.
There are no user rights to exercise with regard to personal data, since none is requested or stored.
DATA TRANSMISSION

There is no data transmission of any kind in Push Box. The game operates fully offline and does not require or initiate any internet connection. As a result, no personal or gameplay-related data is ever sent to MESHY or any third party.

HOW WE PROTECT YOUR PRIVACY

MESHY is dedicated to maintaining your privacy throughout your experience with Push Box. Specifically, we guarantee that:

Push Box is an entirely offline game.
No data (personal or statistical) is collected or stored.
No information is shared or communicated with third parties.
The game does not log or store any gameplay statistics or personal details.
If you have any questions regarding this privacy policy or your experience with Push Box, please feel free to contact us (davinci.dalhi@gmai.com).
